      <h1 class="section-header__title">Introduction</h1>
      <svg width="95" height="9" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="wiggle"><path d="M1.328 7.842c2.317-1.65 4.634-6.594 9.267-6.594 4.634 0 4.634 6.594 9.267 6.594 4.634 0 4.634-6.594 9.268-6.594 4.633 0 4.633 6.594 9.267 6.594 4.633 0 4.633-6.594 9.267-6.594 4.634 0 4.634 6.594 9.267 6.594 4.635 0 4.635-6.594 9.268-6.594 4.634 0 4.634 6.594 9.268 6.594 4.633 0 4.633-6.594 9.267-6.594 4.633 0 6.95 4.945 9.267 6.594" stroke-width="2" stroke="#000" opacity="0.1" fill="none" /></svg>
