  <div class="section-content section-content--conclusion">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p>At it's core, being antifragile is being able to take anything that comes your way and use it to grow. It's an incredible time to be a product designer. We get the chance to reshape whole industries, but with great powers comes great responsibility. We're solving harder and harder problems for an increasing number of people. But we can do better.</p>

      <p>Try new things, shake up your process, introduce randomness and don't make any assumptions. Be Antifragile.</p>
